        <text>
            <body>
                 <p>
                        <persName key="d1e14841" xml:id="d1e141214">G. <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#319548" xml:id="d1e141216">Eduensis</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e14847" xml:id="d1e141219">W. <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#317574" xml:id="d1e141221">Lingonensis</placeName>
                        </persName>, et <persName key="d1e14853" xml:id="d1e141224">W. <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324435" xml:id="d1e141226">Autissiodorensis</placeName>
                        </persName>, Dei gratia episcopi, omnibus <app>
                            <lem wit="#A">presentes</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#a">pręsentes</rdg>
                        </app> litteras inspecturis <lb n="2"/> salutem in Domino. Noverint universi
                        presentes pariter et futuri quod cum inter abbatem et monachos <lb n="3"/>
                        <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e141239">Fonteneti</orgName> ex una
                        parte et nobilem virum <persName key="d1e14859" xml:id="d1e141242">Andream
                            dominum <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324447" xml:id="d1e141244">Espissie</placeName>
                        </persName> ex altera, controver<lb n="4" break="no"/>sia verteretur super
                        hominibus, possessionibus et terris apud <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324475" xml:id="d1e141249">
                            <app>
                                <lem wit="#A">Marmagniam</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#C #a">Marmaniam</rdg>
                            </app>
                        </placeName> existentibus, que nobilis mulier <lb n="5"/>
                        <persName key="d1e14865" xml:id="d1e141257">Hyla de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324962" xml:id="d1e141259">Monte Sancti
                                Johannis</placeName>
                        </persName> et <persName key="d1e14871" xml:id="d1e141263">Johannes</persName>, filius ejusdem, in perpetuam <app>
                            <lem wit="#A">elemosinam</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#a">eleemosynam</rdg>
                        </app> domui <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e141272">Fon<lb n="6" break="no"/>teneti</orgName> dederant et concesserant que etiam a
                        bone memorie <persName key="d1e14878" xml:id="d1e141277">Bernardo, patre
                            ejusdem <persName key="d1e14884" xml:id="d1e141279">Andree</persName>
                        </persName>, abbas <lb n="7"/> et monachi dicebant occupata fuisse, et
                        preterea super trecentis marcis argenti quas predicti abbas <lb n="8"/> et
                        monachi <app>
                            <lem wit="#A">sibi</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#C #a" type="omission"/>
                        </app> a prefato <persName key="d1e14890" xml:id="d1e141292">Bernardo</persName> sepedicti <persName key="d1e14896" xml:id="d1e141295">Andree</persName> patre legatas fuisse asserebant,
                        tandem <lb n="9"/> nobis presentibus et nobilibus viris <persName key="d1e14902" xml:id="d1e141300">Odone duce <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325098" xml:id="d1e141302">Burgundie</placeName>
                        </persName> et <persName key="d1e14908" xml:id="d1e141305">Guidone de
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324440" xml:id="d1e141307">Dompetra</placeName>
                        </persName> et multis aliis in hanc <lb n="10"/> compositionis formam
                        venerunt, quod de trecentis marcis superius nominatis abbas et monachi
                        memorati <lb n="11"/> medietatem habeant, reliquam vero medietatem <persName key="d1e14915" xml:id="d1e141315">Andreas</persName> supradictus. De
                        rebus vero apud <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324475" xml:id="d1e141318">
                            <app>
                                <lem wit="#A">Mar<lb n="12" break="no"/>magniam</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#C #a">Marmaniam</rdg>
                            </app>
                        </placeName> existentibus, de quibus erat controversia, ita fuit statutum
                        quod <persName key="d1e14921" xml:id="d1e141327">Guido, frater <persName key="d1e14927" xml:id="d1e141329">
                                <app>
                                    <lem wit="#A">Andree</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#a">Andreę</rdg>
                                </app>
                            </persName>, <lb n="13"/> canonicus Lingonensis</persName>, res illas
                        tenebit quamdiu vixerit, et post mortem ipsius <persName key="d1e14933" xml:id="d1e141339">Guidonis</persName> ad ecclesiam <lb n="14"/>
                        <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e141344">Fonteneti</orgName> libere
                        et absque omni contradictione revertentur. Tenebit autem res illas <persName key="d1e14939" xml:id="d1e141347">Guido</persName> prefatus nomine <lb n="15"/> ecclesie ab ecclesia <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e141352">Fonteneti</orgName>. Actum anno <app>
                            <lem wit="#A">gratie</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#C">dominice</rdg>
                            <rdg wit="#a" type="omission"/>
                        </app>
                        <num>millesimo cc° <app>
                                <lem wit="#A">terciodecimo</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#C #a">xiii°</rdg>
                            </app>
                        </num>, mense octobri.</p>
                
            </body>
